text: Vanessa Hudgens Changes Up Her Nail Color For Fall Season Saturday, 10 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) Vanessa Hudgens has her hands full with two iced drinks while leaving Alfred’s Coffee and Tea shop in Los Angeles on Wednesday afternoon (October 7).
